142
00:13:30,971 --> 00:13:33,235
<i>Like someone once said...</i>

143
00:13:33,307 --> 00:13:37,505
<i>in L.A. you can find sympathy...</i>

144
00:13:37,578 --> 00:13:39,546
<i>in the dictionary...</i>

145
00:13:39,613 --> 00:13:43,606
