01:24:58,754 --> 01:25:00,779
<i>There were others.</i>

767
01:25:00,857 --> 01:25:03,985
<i>Always others.</i>

768
01:25:04,060 --> 01:25:05,994
<i>Always, Bruce.</i>

769
01:25:07,497 --> 01:25:08,930
<i>Always.</i>

770
01:25:19,742 --> 01:25:22,404
Where have you been?
